graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Control Plane"
        Controller[KServe Controller Manager<br/>Go Operator]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Admission Controller]
        Controller -->|manages| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceService[InferenceService CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1beta1]
        InferenceGraph[InferenceGraph CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        TrainedModel[TrainedModel CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
        ServingRuntime[ServingRuntime CR<br/>serving.kserve.io/v1alpha1]
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Components"
        Agent[Agent Sidecar<br/>Model Downloader]
        Router[Router<br/>Inference Graph]
        StorageInit[Storage Initializer<br/>Init Container]
        PythonSDK[Python SDK<br/>Model Servers]
    end

    subgraph "Model Servers"
        TorchServe[TorchServe<br/>PyTorch]
        TFServing[TF Serving<br/>TensorFlow]
        Triton[Triton<br/>Multi-Framework]
        Custom[Custom Servers<br/>sklearn/xgboost/ONNX]
    end

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        Knative[Knative Serving 0.39.3<br/>Autoscaling]
        Istio[Istio 1.17+<br/>Service Mesh]
        CertManager[cert-manager 1.5+<br/>TLS Certificates]
    end

    subgraph "Storage Backends"
        S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS]
        GCS[GCS Storage<br/>Google Cloud]
        PVC[PVC Storage<br/>Kubernetes]
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| InferenceService
    User -->|creates| InferenceGraph
    User -->|creates| TrainedModel

    InferenceService -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceGraph -->|watched by| Controller
    TrainedModel -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntime -->|watched by| Controller

    InferenceService -->|validated/mutated by| Webhook
    InferenceGraph -->|validated by| Webhook
    TrainedModel -->|validated by| Webhook

    Controller -->|creates| Knative
    Controller -->|creates| Istio
    Controller -->|uses| CertManager

    Controller -->|deploys| Agent
    Controller -->|deploys| Router
    Controller -->|deploys| StorageInit

    Agent -->|downloads models from| S3
    Agent -->|downloads models from| GCS
    StorageInit -->|downloads models from| S3
    StorageInit -->|downloads models from| GCS
    StorageInit -->|mounts from| PVC

    PythonSDK -->|provides| TorchServe
    PythonSDK -->|provides| TFServing
    PythonSDK -->|provides| Triton
    PythonSDK -->|provides| Custom

    Controller -->|deploys| TorchServe
    Controller -->|deploys| TFServing
    Controller -->|deploys| Triton
    Controller -->|deploys| Custom

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceService fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style InferenceGraph fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Knative fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Istio fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertManager fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style S3 fill:#ffd966,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style GCS fill:#ffd966,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
